In addition, gradual shifts of the perovskite peaks with increasing temperature are found in the XRD patterns, which can be ascribed to thermal expansion of the perovskite lattice32. The linear thermal expansion coefficients for different CsxFA1-xPbI3 PQDs are calculated following Eq. 1.1αL=1L0×∂L∂T\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
